The increasing demand for stringent fire and explosion protection in hazardous areas within the mining industry has led to specialist manufacturer and designer of diesel engine flameproof systems, Elgin Flameproofing, launching a new model tractor for underground coal mining applications. This article first appeared in Mining Review Africa Issue 7 2018. It will be published online on the 17th August 2018. You can read the full digital magazine here or subscribe here to receive a print copy